dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains data from the California Tree Seed Zone Map published by CAL FIRE. This map is an inventory system that classifies seeds for collection and planting by psysiographic zones. Fire and Resource Assessment Program (Calif.). (2019). California Tree Seed Zones Map. Fire and Resource Assessment Program (Calif.). Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/sg575tf7838
